S-Paint',\n    thumbnail: './images/ms-paint1.png',\n    description: 'Just For Fun',\n    link: 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/wgrhSCet7Jg'\n  },\n\n  {\n    title: 'Coding Notebook',\n    thumbnail: './images/pieces-of-code.png',\n    description: 'Just For Fun',\n    link: 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/qsCvRFJ1wTE'\n  },\n\n]\n\n\n\nexport default function Video (props) {\n\n  const [videoSrc, setVideoSrc] = useState(projectData[2].link)\n\n\n  return (\n\n    <div className=\"main-video-container\">\n\n      <div className=\"video-screen-container\">\n        <iframe width=\"854\" height=\"480\" src={videoSrc} frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"video-container\" >\n        <div className=\"card\">\n          {projectData.map(project => (\n            <div className=\"video-card\" onClick={() => setVideoSrc(project.link)}>\n              <img className=\"video-thumbnail\" alt=\"video thumbnail\" src={project.thumbnail} />\n              <div className=\"video-description-container\">\n                <h5 className=\"video-card-title\">{project.title}</h5>\n                <h6 className=\"video-card-desc\">{project.description}</h6>\n                <i className=\"play-arrow\"><PlayArrowIcon fontSize=\"large\" /></i>\n              </div>\n            </div >\n          ))}\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\n",{"ruleId":"44","replacedBy":"45"},{"ruleId":"46","replacedBy":"47"},{"ruleId":"44","replacedBy":"48"},{"ruleId":"46","replacedBy":"49"},{"ruleId":"50","severity":1,"message":"51","line":1,"column":17,"nodeType":"52","messageId":"53","endLine":1,"endColumn":25},{"ruleId":"50","severity":1,"message":"54","line":8,"column":8,"nodeType":"52","messageId":"53","endLine":8,"endColumn":18},{"ruleId":"50","severity":1,"message":"55","line":9,"column":8,"nodeType":"52","messageId":"53","endLine":9,"endColumn":17},{"ruleId":"50","severity":1,"message":"56","line":18,"column":10,"nodeType":"52","messageId":"53","endLine":18,"endColumn":20},{"ruleId":"50","severity":1,"message":"57","line":18,"column":22,"nodeType":"52","messageId":"53","endLine":18,"endColumn":42},{"ruleId":"58","severity":1,"message":"59","line":61,"column":9,"nodeType":"60","endLine":61,"endColumn":186},"no-native-reassign",["61"],"no-negated-in-lhs",["62"],["61"],["62"],"no-unused-vars","'useState' is defined but never used.","Identifier","unusedVar","'IconButton' is defined but never used.","'CloseIcon' is defined but never used.","'FilterNone' is defined but never used.","'SettingsInputAntenna' is defined but never used.","jsx-a11y/iframe-has-title","<iframe> elements must have a unique title property.","JSXOpeningElement","no-global-assign","no-unsafe-negation"]